10 Jan 2010 05:37






Disposing of the bodies and explaining the absence of 318. It seems to be pretty standard practice to eliminate anybody that was too closely tied to an SCP (the monks certainly qualify), and since it'd be impractical to actually track down every single person that had heard of 318/318-1, it's easier to just make it look like they'd been destroyed.





